on of several\nsymmetries and can be relatively easily implemented in the standard\nself-consistent mean-field calculations, including those required for the\nparameter adjustments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2015 19:41:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Nov 2015 13:48:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-17"}
